────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DATA ATTRIBUTION NOTICE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
This software retrieves and processes data from the following sources.
Users must comply with their respective terms of use:

  • GPM IMERG V06 — NASA / JAXA
    https://gpm.nasa.gov/data/imerg

  • SRTMGL1 v003 — NASA / USGS
    https://lpdaac.usgs.gov/products/srtmgl1v003/

  • SoilGrids v2 — ISRIC — World Soil Information
    https://www.isric.org/explore/soilgrids

  • ESA WorldCover v200 — ESA / VITO
    https://esa-worldcover.org/en

  • Sentinel-2 SR Harmonized — ESA / Google
    https://sentinel.esa.int/web/sentinel/missions/sentinel-2

  • FAO GAUL (2015) — Food and Agriculture Organization
    https://www.fao.org/geonetwork

All data is accessed via the Google Earth Engine platform:
  https://earthengine.google.com
